Privacy Policy for SQLite Database Editor

Last Updated: November 4th ,2024

Introduction

Thank you for using SQLite Database Editor by CtrlY>CtrZ. We value your privacy and are committed to ensuring that your personal information remains secure. This Privacy Policy describes the data the App may access or collect, how we use this information, and the steps we take to protect your privacy. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices. By using this App, you accept the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

1. Information Collection and Use

SQLite Database Editor is designed to operate as a local utility. It does not require any personal information from you, nor does it transmit data about your usage off your device.

2. Permissions Required

To function effectively, the App requires specific permissions. Here is a description of these permissions and how they support its features:

Storage Access: This permission allows the App to read and modify SQLite database files stored on your device. It enables you to open, import, and save database files, ensuring you can make edits directly within the App.

File Read/Write Access: The App may read from and write to your device’s storage to save changes made to SQLite files and allow exporting of updated data files, enabling you to manage and back up your database files as needed.


3. Data Security

All data handled by SQLite Database Editor remains on your device and is managed solely by you. The App does not store or retain any data on external servers. We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to outside parties.

4. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally to reflect changes in the App’s features, requirements, or applicable laws. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about our practices. Your continued use of the App following any changes signifies your acceptance of those updates.

5. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at ctrlygreaterthanctrlz@gmail.com.


This Privacy Policy is intended to provide a clear understanding of how SQLite Database Editor handles your data and respects your privacy. Thank you for trusting us with your database management needs.
